    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A range of reddish brown colors resembling the color of roofer's red paint, also called "red oxide," used as a primer for exterior metal surfaces.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000009521/Color: Universal Language and Dictionary (1976)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>指一特定範圍的紅褐色色彩，色近於屋頂紅油漆，亦稱「氧化鐵紅」，用作金屬表面的底漆。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
